{"tid":1949064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企 雪櫃 大比拼","createTime":"2020-03-29T11:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T00:54:45.000Z","uid":80222,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8f5687021fc8917884d6945764fadc6eefcb33","tid":1949064,"uid":80222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"話說我老母當雪櫃係萬能保鮮箱<br />\n情況由我出世開始維持到依家<br />\n我想放盒維他奶都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講雪櫃無自己嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬年食物藥材都起晒雪櫃嘅深處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想幫佢清理吓就比佢屌到屎忽開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔信有人屋企塞嘢多過我屋企雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋磚引玉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PoEnGeC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPoEnGeC.jpg&h=3cd410cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AovqD1i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAovqD1i.jpg&h=35efccc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd2b2f37d329449b00df413b94b96819b036a388","tid":1949064,"uid":151479,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"好撚憎啲野食原件連埋膠袋塞入雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2782ddb6daed9d017797d0a3dc6b682f6acb5db7","tid":1949064,"uid":84043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"買多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d345ebc55b5b9949eacda3cff8f474b6138d1779","tid":1949064,"uid":80222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd2b2f37d329449b00df413b94b96819b036a388","tid":1949064,"uid":151479,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"好撚憎啲野食原件連埋膠袋塞入雪櫃<img src=\"/as